# Squad View UI/UX Enhancement

## Goal
Enhance the squad view to allow gradually adding people into a squad for easier planning with a dynamic UI/UX. The UI should have 2 columns (tasks vs squad tasks) and dynamically update as people are added.

## Checklist
- [ ] Understand current squad/daily meeting implementation
- [ ] Design the dynamic "Squad View" UI/UX (2 columns, gradual addition of personnel)
- [ ] Create implementation plan (`implementation_plan.md`)
- [ ] Request user review for the plan
- [ ] Implement the new 2-column layout in `DailyMeetingView` / `SquadView`
- [ ] Implement logic to gradually add personnel and compute shared/individual tasks
- [ ] Verify the UI behavior (overview tasks, shared tasks, other tasks)
- [ ] Create walkthrough documenting the changes
